\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  to Cambridge?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well my father's occupation.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Could you tell me a bit more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
He was a stonemason and he used to work on churches and big buildings. And wherever those buildings were, so he went and he would never keep two homes going, he always took us away, school or no school he took us away. So we should be together.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was he as it were self-employed - hired himself out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. No. He was - with a firm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 With a firm that did work over quite a wide area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes. Yes, big firm they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Where did you go to from Cambridge?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 We went - I went to Woodford Green. School at Woodford Green on - right on the Green, the church school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was the move from Cambridge the same reason?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes. Once again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You were about nine a when you went there, how old were you when you left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Say about - ten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Not very long there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
