\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 We moved once, twice - three times in West Norwood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You mean you had four different houses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes. There a different.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Why did you move house in West Norwood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well - probably - we can say - better accommodation you know. As the family grew up you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You mean it was better quality accommodation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You were one of a family of four?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Where did you come in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 I was top.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Who was the next one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Brother.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 How much younger was he than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Two years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Then the next?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Next one was - sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 How much younger was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 She's - ten years younger than me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 And then there was one more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 One more sister. She'd be about twelve years younger than me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You told me your father was about twenty-four when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you know where he was born and educated?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes. Cambridge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 This stonemason work, had that always been his work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you know if there was any period in which he did anything else at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, none at all. In fact he made the gravestone for my brother's grave. Yes, in Colchester.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You had a brother that passed away when you were in Colchester did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 He was schoolboy, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 That was your only brother then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you ever remember him being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes, quite a lot. Quite a lot. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 
In the days when times were very. very bad. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
I've known him to walk to London with coppers in his pocket and rather than spend them he used to walk. There and walk back. And then come back without a job probably.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was that when he was no longer working for the same fire?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh he worked for several firms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was he ever out of work for quite a long period?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What was about the longest do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well they were shut out once, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 How long did that last?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 That was some months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you know if he got any sort of strike pay or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. There was no such thing as strike pay then, those days. You got a little small amount from the union if you were lucky but 
- that was nothing much, a matter of shillings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember that or did you just hear tell about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh no, I remember him being in the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Where were you living when that happened?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 West Norwood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember what difference it made at that time to the family standard of living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Very much say, we - only had half or quarter of the food we used to have.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What sort of things were cut out for example?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh lots of things you couldn't afford in those days. not - I me
an general things like butter, bacon and all that kind of stuff you couldn't afford that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you know if your father had any savings he drew on at these times or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, he had no opportunity to save. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did they get any financial help from any charity or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. My people didn't anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you know where your mother came from, was she also Cambridge?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 She - no, she was born in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 Arundel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 , Sussex.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Had she a job before she }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13699159 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did she ever work after marriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. My father was rather }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 inclined}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  to be independent and he wouldn't allow her to work you see. It wasn't - it wasn't done in those days you see. Woman didn't go to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you think she would ever liked to have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well, probably a lot of women in those days would have liked but it's - just that it was an unwritten law that - stayed at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 When you said he was independent, what other forms did this take?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well he wouldn't - receive help. In fact there was 
a lot of men like that in those days. No, it was - beneath their dignity to accept any - they go and walk and try and find a job you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 When you say he walked to London, that was from West Norwood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 About eight - eight miles each way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 I suppose in winter they were often not able to work because of the weather?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 When he had these periods of not working do you remember what he used to do, if he had any hobbies or anything he used to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well, he had an allotment 
but - he had little time on that because his time was taken up in walking backwards and forwards to London in hopes of getting a job.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Stonemasonry is a sort of top trade isn't it in a way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well it was a good - a very good profession in those days, yes. It was quite a skilled job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
In West Norwood can you tell me how many rooms there were in the house you lived in the longest, which house did you live in the longest there, the first one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes, a kitchen, a sitting room, two bedrooms and a scullery.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was that the first house you went to, or the second or third?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well they were all the same
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did anyone else besides your parents and your sisters ever live with you in West Norwood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Never had a lodger?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did your mother ever pay anybody to help her in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you know how she managed about her washing, did she do it at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes. In the bathtub. We had no bathroom you see. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you know if your mother made or bought the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well she made a lot - most of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did she have a swing machine then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 My sister used to have one but - later years but I'm not sure whether my mother had one or not, I don't think she did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 They sewed a lot by hand then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 When she bought new clothes would that have teen top clothes like coats?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you know where she bought them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well - most of those were in - round about Brixton way in - that's a little market place Brixton was in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Would she go up and shop there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes. Penny on the tram.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did she take you with her or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. She didn't go very often because we could most of what we wanted in - in West Norwood itself. If you wanted anything specia
l you went into Brixton, pennyworth on the tram - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 horse trams}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 How long was the journey then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well they used to change horses half way you see. And - I suppose it took - ooh, perhaps three quarters of an hour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember whether she belonged to any clothing clubs or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 did}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  she pay cash down for something when she bought it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well it's cash down most of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 She didn't pay into clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 She used to be a member of the Co-op I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was that in Brixton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, in West Norwood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember whether she ever bought anything secondhand at all at a rummage sale or anything like that in the way of clothing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, because rummage sales were very - they weren't thought of much in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 You didn't buy there if you could help it you mean?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
No. People used to wear their clothes almost out you see before they - they hadn't got the money to keep going buying like they have today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 So she never bought anything secondhand?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What about mending the clothes, did she do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you know if she bought clothes for a special occasion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well there was very few special occasions because in - in our time - when people }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13699159 Married}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  and they had a family - they never thought of leaving 
that family alone with anybody else to look after it until the children were grown up they never went out, my parents never went to a theatre or went to holiday or anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 They never went out in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, no, no. The day that my younges
t sister reached probably about fourteen, my father called us in one day and he said now, mother and I have looked after you all these years, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 we\rquote re}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  now going to enjoy ourselves because you're capable of looking after yourselves and they used to begin to go out then to theatres and - but there was no such thing as }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 baby sitters}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  then, they weren't thought of. Not even grandmother - was no }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 babysitter}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you have a grandmother nearby in West Norwood at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh no, not at that time. No, she was dead, she was ninety - ninety-four I think or ninety-five when she died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Where had she lived?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Cambridge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You don't remember her looking after you at all or did she on some occasions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well - I suppose - I can remember her quite well Like mo
st grandmothers she used to think a lot of the grandchildren you see. We could go in and out as we liked and there was a cupboard there with a - always a tin with a seed cake in and help yourself you see. But as far as }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 babysitters}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  went they - they weren't thought of. They didn't go out and leave them like they do today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You were quite a bit older than the two girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You weren't left in charge at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. Oh no, no. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did they aim to get new clothes for everybody at a certain season of the year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
Well generally I suppose Easter. Of course, you had then what is known - what we call today lounges, they're really the - the old sitting rooms you see. And you only went in the sitting room once a week and that was on Sundays.
 And you had to put your best clothes on to go in there. No such thing as going in in your sports clothes and - this sort of thing. You had to dress - dress and sit }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10686276\charrsid15798853 there}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  and behave yourself Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Your family never used it except on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 That's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Not even on a birthday party of anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Very seldom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Can you remember where your shoes were bought, were they also bought at Brixton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well some - when we were in that neighbourhood, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Were they bought ready made?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Can you remember how they were mended?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Mended, well father used to do most of them. Most of the fathers used to mend the shoes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember if your father did anything in the house in the way of cleaning or cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 None at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You never remember him cooking a thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What about washing up, did he ever do that, or drying up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 I never saw him do much of that either.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Can you ever remember any occasion when he did that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What about making the fires, did he ever do that or did your mother do it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Mother used to do most of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Things like wallpapering or decorating or repairs, did he do that type of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well - there wasn't much of that done really in those 
days. The man used to go to work, come home, clean his shoes ready for the next day and - that was it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 They were such long hours weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh long, yes, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember him doing anything for you or your younger sisters or you
r brother when he was alive, in the way of looking after you like putting you to bed or dressing you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 That was mother's job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 That's it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Things like telling you a story or reading to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What about taking you out, did he ever take you out anywhere?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Occasional, yes, he used to take us out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Would your mother come too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. Sometime she would, not very often. The mother's jobs were generally reckoned to be - with the children in the home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 The shops were open much longer hours then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes. Yes. You could go down and get a Sunday joint at eleven or half past eleven to twelve o'clock on Saturday nights at Brixton.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did your mother ever do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh many times, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 They'd auction them off would they?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 That's right. Get a leg for about two shillings. Leg of lamb for about two shillings. Glad to get rid of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did she ever go shopping and he stay behind and look after you or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You told me about having to do a little job on a Saturday morning, could you repeat that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
Well - I was the - the top boy if you like, of the school and I was also Captain of the school football and - we used to have a match every Saturday morning against another school. And
 it was always my job to collect our team and take them, you see, go with them. Because the master used to give me the money for - say a penny or whatever it is, for fares you see. Penny }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 
bus rides}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  and all that. Well - I always had a job to do on Saturday m
orning, that was the knives forks and spoons on the board with the - powder stuff. And I had to clean them to the satisfaction of my father before I was allowed to go to football match. And the rest of the boys didn't - they didn't suffer that way, they w
e
re all outside knocking - keep knocking, aren't you coming, aren't you coming, aren't you ready, and so on. And when I'd done I had to say to my father, I've finished dad. He'd come and look at them and he'd take each one up, if it wasn't to his satisfact
ion I had to go; over it again. In the meantime the boys were all waiting outside for me. Anyway we got over it eventually I suppose. Didn't do me any harm. Neither did the cane at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 So that was your regular job then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Anything else you had to do say on other days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Were you expected to clean your own boots or did father do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 I - later - in later years as we got along towards say thirteen and fourteen you had to clean your own because he always used 
to clean his the high before ready for the next day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 But when you were sort of nine, ten or eleven he did them did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Up to that time, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 They were more difficult to clean then weren't they?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes. No, and of course the leather was different, it was all coarse - very coarse leather - schoolboy boots.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you have to do anything like fetching milk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. I did a paper round in the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 When did you start that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 When I was about - ten. Up to about - half past fiv
e every morning. Do the papers - walk - two miles, well, mile anyway to get to the shop. And sort my own papers out. Take them round to the customers, which covered a good distance 'cos I didn't ride a cycle. And - one of my customers - was - you may not 
know this gentleman but he was a well known man on the music hall. George Cherwin, the black eyed Kaffir. No. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 He used to sing - I'm but a poor, poor blind boy. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 And he - I used to serve him. Well then I'd finish the paper round, finish out the remaining time
 until I went to school helping the milkman. And all those little extra coppers used to come in very useful. I got a golden half sovereign for a Christmas Box from George Cherwin.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was he friendly to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes, he used to have all the boys in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 Easter time}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
, Good Fridays and hot cross bun days, we used to have to go into the kitchen, housekeeper or maid, what she call - and we used to have tea, oh the milk boy, the paper boy, the greengrocer boy and all the errand boys you know. Have this hot cross bun.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was he a bachelor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 He was at that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Were the boys quite thrilled?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 I suppose he was well known own like some of the television personalities are?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes, he was very well known. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Can you remember what you got paid for that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
Oh - I think it was - I think it was shilling a week. And that was very good because the - gentleman who used to run the shop, he was a very - not over - religious but he was a church man, and he never sold Sunday papers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 So it was just Monday to Saturday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Monday to Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you do the milk on a Sunday as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh that was on Sunday as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What did you get for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Few coppers - about fourpence, fivepence.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 A week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You went out at half past five, did you go home for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
Yes. Yes. There was no time limit like there is today. See, you're not allowed to employ a newspaper boy under a certain age today. And if you employ him you - you mustn't - you can't employ him, only for a certain length of time. In my time - that -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What did you do with the money you received?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well used to buy a bun now and then and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You were able to keep it for yourself then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 For a few pennies - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Your parents didn't expect you to hand any over?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was it your own idea to get the jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes. I went and got the job on my own and - my father was very annoyed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Why was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Because he said that there's no - at that time there was no need for me to go to work. When there was he would tell me. Anyway -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 But he didn't make you give it up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 As you've got the job on your own - I went with another choirboy you see, as you've got the job on your own, he said, I'll se
e you darn well keep it. First morning I got up like a lark, it's a new toy. Second morning - I was very late getting up, sleepy. And he came in, he pulled the clothes off me, he said, come on, you got the job, he said, now you go and keep it. I - I neede
d that once, that's all.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 He sounds a good father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well he never - he never hit us in any way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 But he was strict and he had his standards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 I'd believe I told you when you were here the other day that - an occasion when I was a choirboy we used to have toilet in the }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10686276\charrsid15798853 garden.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  And I went out there one day and I used to - like most choirboys we had a quiet puff of a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 cigarette}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  or - so and he'd followed me out and he came in and he said, mother, I believe that boy's smokes. She said, no, he wo
uldn't smoke. Of course mother wouldn't have it you see. So he said, son, do you smoke? I didn't lie to him, I said, yes brown paper dad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was it brown paper then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, it was a cigarette. So he said, oh, right-o. So he goes in the sitting room,; 
comes back with a cigar. Now, he said, I'm sure you'll enjoy that, he said, now you smoke that in front of me, enjoy yourself, I'll have one with you. Of course I had this cigar and was beginning to turn and mother began to get a little bit - said he was 
cruel. He said, no, he said, that won't hurt him. In the end I had to give way, I had to go outside you see. I never smoked for years after that. That was his way of punishing me, he didn't - hit me or grumble, just - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember any other occasions when he punished you for anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 
Well - at a later year - when I was about seventeen - eighteen, I joined the Territorials which was the volunteers or more or less those days. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
And - he used to keep a tight rein on me for getting in. I wasn't allowed out after ten until I'd turned twenty-one. I never had a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 door key}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  until I was turned twenty-one. And if I wasn't - if I - went out anywhere I - he used to say, what time are you coming in son? I used to say perhaps, oh half past nine. He'd be ther
e in the room at half past nine, if I wasn't in he'd be out looking for me. And my mother's often told me that - she's covered up for me. 'Cos as father tuned to go up that way I must have come in the other way and she - she used to say, oh I've been in f
or a long time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 If you asked him?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Whatever time I said I had to be in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 But it had to be ten did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. Whatever time I said. He said, don't tell me ten if you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 intend}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  to be twelve.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 But he would let you stay out 'til twelve?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes, when I got a bit older, of course I used to go to Territorial dances.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 But he did want to know the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 He still - up to I was twenty-one he wanted to know the time. When I reached twenty-one - he called me in. He said, son, he said, yo
u've now reached the age of twenty-one. Nothing gives me more pleasure than to let you have a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 door key}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
. But, he said, remember this is your home and don't abuse it. That's what he said. Quite a ceremonial thing. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was he quite a formal person in his way of talking to people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes, yes, yes. He was quite all right. Just, this he said, never forget this is your home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was he particular too with your young sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well - he was - no, not so much then because they all had }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 door keys}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  before they were twenty-one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Why was that do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 I haven't a clue.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 I think the younger ones get away with more in a family in that way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes. Oh my elder sister used to come in quite late.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 And he didn't mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 The sa
me with cards. My mother would never have cards in the house. When I came on leave when I was in the army in the firs war, I brought two or three colleagues with me and suggested a game of cards, so - she said, oh no. When I came the second time she said 
t
o me, come on son, we'll have a game of cards today. I said, how long's this been. Well she'd joined the - Co-op and she used to go to Women's whist drives you know, she'd take a liking, she was playing whist at a whist drive a week before she died actual
ly. In Devonshire.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did your father play cards too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Had he not disapproved of them in the way she'd done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh no. Oh no. I don't know why she did really, she - it wasn't - no religious - no, no, no, not at all, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember being sent up to bed without supper or anything of that type?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes. Yes. Yes. Yes, I've been sent up to bed without supper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 By your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did your mother ever do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Mother didn't, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you ever remember your mother punishing you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 It was all done by father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 She used to cover up for you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You say you never got a caning from him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. No, he never - never - he could do it by word.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Not a box on the ear, nothing like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 And your mother didn't do that either?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
One day - he called me and I was in the sitting room, and I said what they do say today and that is, what for? And all he said was, I called you, come and see. So when I came in he said, next time
 I call you I want you, remember that, he said, and come. That's all he did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Were they particular about bedtime when you were younger?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well I think that ceased probably when I was about six or seven - and after - that it began to get a bit later. Never very late but just -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
As they put the time on were they quite particular about it, you had to be in bed by a certain time or did they not mind if you stayed up late provided you were indoors?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, they used to like to see you in bed by a certain time. Until you got a bit older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember if your mother put you to bed or if you put yourself to bed when you were little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, she used to say, up to bed, and that's it, you went up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Would she come up then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 She'd come up later to see you were in bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What about when you were very small?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 And she'd pull the clothes back to see you hadn't - still hadn't got your socks - stockings on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you ever remember her putting you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you share the bed and the bedroom or did you have one to yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
No, well in Colchester I only had the brother you see. So we only wanted the one room for the two of us. When the sisters came along of course we had to get - house with separate rooms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You didn't share with your sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 When you were in West Norwood, did you say two bedrooms or three?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 How did you manage then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 In the last house there were three with a - two and a small, what they call a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 box room}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  those d
ays, 'cos we had no bathroom you see. Of course when bath time was on, well everybody else had to be out you see, your sisters had to be out or vice versa.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Before you had the house with three bedrooms were your sisters born then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, we went in because they were there then. It was easier to get a place then than what it is today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 People did seem to be able to move more easily didn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well you could rent 1 you could rent places.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you have to take the younger ones out in a pram at all or look after them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember doing anything at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
I can only remember them - at quite an early age when - I used to go out with my younger brother and I can remember then we had a big dog and the dog used to do more of the guarding of the children - we two children than -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You used to take him with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You didn't have to tell them stories or read to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Or look after them or feed them, your mother did all that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember them doing anything for you, like running errands for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, I don't think so, not to that extent anyway, not -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You were quite a lot older, did you play with them at all or have anything much to do with them when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well they - my sister used to play the piano and I - when I started the violin you see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You'd play duets would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 mm. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 
Just for a little while until - I suppose I began to think of other things, football and one thing and another - I gave the violin up.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Were you keen on the violin for a while?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 I was in the school - used to be taught at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 That must have been quite unusual in those days, to be able to be taught the violin at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 They used to have a half an hour or hour set }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 aside}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  for - music.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you have a piano at home then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You didn't learn that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. Only by ear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did your mother or father play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. My sister did. Both sisters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did the family ever have a sing-song?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes. That used to be the Sunday evening - ritual that did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You did it most Sunday evenings then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well if you went out in those days you had to do something, recite, sing or tell a story or - you had to do something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh I didn't mind what it was. I used to sing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you ever recite?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Sometimes yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did people come to your house sometimes on a Sunday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes, used to perhaps have an aunt or somebody like that just tu
rn up. That was set aside for visitors, you know, Sundays. Not like today, they just go out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 It must have been lovely having a piano and singing, did you enjoy it at the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes. My }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 wife\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  family used to do more than we I think. Musical they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you ever go to anything like the Messiah or a concert or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 I didn't personally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did your mother or father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 They were at home with the children weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 That's right, they never went out you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 There weren't bathrooms in those houses in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You had to organise so that the girls were out when the boys had a bath and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 We had a bathtub. A big bath tub. And the water was in the kitchen. In 
the copper. You had to base it out of the copper into - and - when it was my turn well then my sisters had to make themselves scarce and - likewise when it was their turn I had to make myself scarce.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 How often did you go through this business?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well - probably it was on the go every night I expect for one or the other. It was only a - you know - copper didn't hold a great amount.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You didn't have a system of once a week, you had it more than that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well, you had to have one a week anyway. At least one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 When you said your sisters had to go out and this sort of thing, was this on the same night, or would they have it different nights?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes, you'd probably wait 'til they go to bed or something like that you see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 And keep putting fresh hot water in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Then lock the - stairs door you see so they couldn't - 'til you'd finished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What about clean clothing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 I used to have clean clothing quite frequently, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was it on a special day you'd have it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, Sundays mostly. That was the - dressing up day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you eat in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Were there ever any times when you ate in the front room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Most unlikely. Most unlikely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 If you were there on Sunday it wouldn't be for eating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, you'd have - you eat in the kitchen and go into the - sitting room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Where did your mother cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 In the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember what type of cooking equipment she had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes, a Larwood range.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 That's solid fuel is it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes. I don't think there's - I don't know whether they're still made today I wouldn't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did it have an oven?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes, oven, yes. Oh yes. And lot of people - still wish they had those ovens too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you all have breakfast together in your family or did you have it at separate times?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
Well in - my particular family - we were fairly regular - all together. Sundays - or Saturdays - Sat - Sundays my father used to go for a walk before dinner. And he used to call in and see some of his - allotment fri
ends, have a drink and come home to dinner. That was his regular routine.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 On weekday mornings what time would breakfast be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well - you had to get to school at nine o'clock. So it would be somewhere about eightish I should think. My father of co
urse would have been gone to work since five o'clock - half past five.
