\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did he grow enough for the whole family or did you have to buy some?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes, used to grow quite enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10686276\charrsid15798853 Were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 there fruit trees there too or just vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, mostly vegetables. Tomatoes and stuff you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Any fruit at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Probably some currants and - raspberries.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you work on the allotment at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, I didn't - I did very little -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Would he have liked you to or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 I had no - interest init.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember if your mother or father ever bought }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 tinned}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  fruit or vegetables at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 They did buy tinned fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You were saying there were hard times when food had to be cut down because of lack of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you ever remember seeing your mother having less so the family could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes, many times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What about your father, was he given more as a man who had to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, he used to give up a lot too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 A lot of people got extra things like rabbits from poaching, did your father ever do anything like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 I never knew - getting any from a poacher.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did he ever go out himself and set a snare?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you have tinned meat at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, the only tinned meat I had was when the war broke out, 1914/18 war. The only tinned meat I had. Bully beef.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 But you don't remember having corned beef at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Were you allowed to talk at a meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Not with your mouth full though.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 But conversation wasn't discouraged?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. You had to get on with your meal but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Could you choose what you wanted to eat or did you have to eat what was cooked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well you generally had what was - wha
t was on the table. If you said you didn't like it well that was just too bad, you had to eat it or go without.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 If you took a portion of food and left some of it what would they say to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 It wasn't - in very good favour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was it just thrown out if it was left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well it was generally given to the birds or something or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You didn't have hens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, we didn't personally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Could you ask for a second helping if you wanted one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You could do but mother used to say well do you really want it you know. Don't leave it, don't waste it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 But you could ask, you didn't have to wait 'til you were offered?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What about if there was something on the table you wanted like the salt could you ask for it to be passed to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well - mother used to try and get you to - be - have decent table manners, to ask - somebody to pass it you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What about how you sat at the table, did they teach you that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well you sat there but you had to behave yourself. Not fool around.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Holding your knife, fork and spoon, were they particular about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes. Not to stick - with the knife sticking up in the air.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Could you bring a toy or a book to the table during a meal?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. They didn't like it anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 When could you leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well, you generally left the table when people had finished and you used to ask permission to get down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember if you all sat at the same table for a meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you always have the same places?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 How was the meal served, some people served from the pots onto the plates, others put it into dishes on the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well when we were children it was served straight from the pots, onto the plates. Depends what
 you had of course, I mean, what meal it was. But anything like potatoes, greens or stew I mean was all come out of the pot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 She didn't put dished on the table to you to help yourself from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 When your sisters were very small, how did they manage for their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well I can only remember them being fed in the normal way by mother that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Where did they sit then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well we had a high chair, if you were that small, but otherwise you sat where you were put.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 They did have a high chair did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well if you were lucky.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did she have one on her lap during a meal while she fed it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well it'd be very small to be on her lap.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You were saying how your mother would cover up for you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes, many times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was she an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well I suppose she was, yes, she wasn't difficult.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Could you take your little worries to her, that sort of thing, if you were worried - confide in her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh I don't think you'd do that, not take any worries to her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was she an affectionate sort of mother, did she show affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well in her way - yes - she used to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What was her way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well she wasn't all over you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was your father the sort of person you told if you were worried about anything or did you keep it to yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. He wasn't one that you could - tell him much you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 They weren't like that so much then so people say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you think there was more or a distance, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 respect}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  and distance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You had to more or less find your own way you see, as you grew up you weren't told half the things they're told today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Was he also not the type to be all over you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you talk much to him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Not - not a great deal, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
Can you remember if your parents brought you up to behave towards your sisters or brother, did they have certain ways they thought you should behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, I don't think they had any particular way, not - we just grew up in the - in the house together and that was all.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 They didn't say you should do this or you should do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 More by example?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 If another child hit you did they say you should hit back or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well - how can we answer tha
t now. I only had one instance when I was at school in Cambridge - when a so called bully of the school went for another boy and I stepped in and I knocked him out. And I can remember, later in the day, a policeman came round to the door and I thought we'
r
e going to get into trouble. The policeman simply said to me he said, remember - if you hit anybody again, don't hit them quite as hard as you've done this one. Yes. Well of course - that stood me in good stead later on in later years when I used to box i
n the army you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You took up boxing in the army?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes. Well I used to go in for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You don't remember your mother or father saying anything in that way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did they know about this incident?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember what they said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 My mother was very - upset about it because - she thought I might grow into a - a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 vicious}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  man. But it - I didn't have to do it again, you know, I say I - I took up boxing and was taught by a professional. And - well - I didn't do
 it with any view to any gain or any money - just - the sort of recreation.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember what your father said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 I always thought it'd be very nice to know how to defend yourself if you were attacked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember what your father said about the incident?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh well he - all he said was, well, he said, next time you might get it done to you. So be prepared.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Your father seemed to have very definite ideas about the way of bringing children up
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well yes, I would say that, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What were the sort of things they felt generally important in life to teach their children do you thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well the one great thing that they used to try and get into us, and sisters as well - that - well never forget your home, always remember 
your home, never abuse it. That was his great thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 He mentioned that quite a few times did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What kind of people do you think they }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 hoped}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  you'd grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well I - I don't think they thought on those lines at all. Really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 What do you think they thought the good person was, the sort of values they had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
Well I should say that - they used to try and look on life as something which - was very nice if you knew how to behave yourself during life, not get yourself into trouble in any way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember if they had any views about swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well, swearing was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10686276\charrsid15798853 taboo,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  I mean, if - it wasn't looked upon with any good - grace at all. See, because we followed on an age where of course - you didn't have to do any wrong at all did you, the old Victorian age. Or else you soon got punished.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Were you allowed to join in when your father and mother were talking to friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, it used to be, speak when you're spoken to. That used to be the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 These ideas you got about how to behave, would you say you got them more from your mother or more from your father or equally from both?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well I - as far as I was concerned it came more from my mother I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Can you remember a birthday in your schooldays, did you have a party ever or anything at all to mark the day as different?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 My people were never one to have many parties at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you ever have a friend in to tea or some little thing or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you have a present or was a birthday just like any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 
It was just like any other day only you - very, very lucky if you got a present, especially with circumstances as they were with people out of work they just couldn't run to these things.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 So you wouldn't expect a present?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. Well you would expect it but you wouldn't get it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Anything special to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
No. No. If you were in a family where - say the father was in permanent employment and that sort of thing, not - not worried by strikes or put offs 
or lock outs, well they - they had the money - the few coppers extra needed for these little things, but you hadn't got it if you were in a family where the father was out of work quite a bit you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Can you remember whether Christmas Day was a special day at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
Oh-oh, Christmas Day. Hang your stocking up and find two or three nuts and an orange and a penny at the bottom, that was your - that was your lot. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Anything special to eat on Christmas or just the same sort of food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well, you probably -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you have a Christmas dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes, we didn't have things like turkeys and all that sort of thing, just a little bit - probably extra, a few nuts - if they could }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 afford}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you go out on Christmas Day, visiting relatives or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well as - as school children, no. But }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 as}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  teenagers, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You would go out on your own or with your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well my - my parents not being one to have parties I used to - in the teenage time I used to spend my time with 
my wife's people, because they were a big party - always went in for a party they did.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 So you'd go to Christmas parties there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 You didn't have them at your own home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Would you go to parties there on Christmas Day or was it round the season that you'd have the parties?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well there again you - as a child - children, you were home. In }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 teenage}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  I used to spend it there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 The actual day there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did relations come and call on Christmas Day at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well in my case, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Do you remember your parents playing any games with you at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Well not - not as such, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you have snake and ladders or ludo in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh we had snakes and ladders, yes, ludo and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did they play it with your or did you play among yourselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Very seldom they played.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Ball games or outdoor games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 My people were not the entertaining kind you see in any way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did your father ever knock a ball around in the yard with you or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. The only thing he did with me was put a pair of boxing gloves on and - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 spar}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  about in the garden, yes, until mother - got cross because he made my nose bleed.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 So he was keen on boxing too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Yes, he used to - in his younger days he us
ed to do a lot. In his younger days as a teenager - he used to travel round with a boxing club that used to go from village to village you see. In the way you - sort of took on anybody and if you were unlucky you just - went on your back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Must have been pretty tough in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
That's why he always tried to instill into me that it's a good thing to be able to - defend yourself if you were attached. Now when to hit and how to hit and where to hit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 So you were saying you went to the Barrack School?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Barrack Street school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 And you remember your father taking you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
Well he - the Boer War was on and he used to take me on his shoulder, 'soc I was only - what - six, seven, might have been six and a half. And he used to take me on h
is shoulder and hold me there and watch the soldiers leave the barracks and go to the station ready for going abroad, with all their read coats on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you enjoy that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Oh yes. Yes. Never thought that I'd have the same thing to do myself in later
 years. But that was when we were living in Colchester. That - he used to take me to Wivenhoe with him fishing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Out in a boat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, just go off the side of the bank you see. And - I used to become very naughty and restive and I used to throw ston
es at the float and I used to get a little flick every now and then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did he take you fishing after you left Colchester?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, we didn't do much more after that. But he used to do in his younger days, he used to do ice skating on the River Cam. And
 they used to have races you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 Did you ever do ice skating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, I didn't. But he used to have quite - quite a lot - good number of ice }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 skates}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  - shoes and those things. Used to be }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13189204\charrsid15798853 polishing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853  them up and greasing then up one thing and another, I can always remember him doing that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 They used to put grease on them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 
Yes, used to put some sort of grease on. I wasn't old enough to know the particular technical term but - he used to go racing quite a lot on the River Cam, and he was also a
 member of - a club which went village boxing as they call it, you know, the rough stuff.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14966536 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 That was in Cambridge too was it?
