\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No. She used to have the job of washing all the dirty football clothes - knickers.
