pboard at the end of a sitting room, a little old cottage sitting room, and there was always a tin there with a cake in. A seed cake. She used to have them all cut ready and she said, now when you come, no matter when it is, if I'm not here you help yours
elf and take a piece of cake home. Now that was the difference between the two.
