\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2884641 PC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9845573\charrsid15798853 No, no. As a schoolboy. And teenager with my wife's people.
